1. create a new file as "extraFile" on github manually
   use fetch command to bring to local
   so the origin/main get forward.
   "git fetch"
                                da5f8bc (origin/main, origin/HEAD) Create some extraFile
                                243f38f (HEAD -> main) git ignore
                                a161c5a git ignore
                                e1d83c6 fetch

2. use merge to move our current branch
   "git merge origin/main"
   it will be a fast forward merge (we have not any deviation)

                               da5f8bc (HEAD -> main, origin/main, origin/HEAD) Create some extraFile
                               243f38f git ignore
                               a161c5a git ignore
                               e1d83c6 fetch
                               eb28f26 credential
                               765d208 Initial commit

Note: we can use
      "git branch -vv"
      to compare current branch and upstream branch on server!